{"tid":2312287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根據社會主義法系　中國修憲違反公約　香港可不予承認","createTime":"2020-12-04T18:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T20:12:27.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb67cb855f0d376b9e3b4aa7985abb220d49582","tid":2312287,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T18:52:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2907318772837528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2907318772837528&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wyTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=5daf6898\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2907318772837528</a><br />\n<br />\n啲法師亂講「法系」，攞「社會主義法律」做萬能key擋箭牌。咁我咪直接搬蘇聯愛沙尼亞嘅修憲分歧理論出來囉，同一「法系」呀。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我係香港最權威法律學者，但我都有啲驚訝冇人講過呢點，香港啲所謂法學院嘅學術勞工真係唔會開新方向。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2907428436159895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2907428436159895&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wyTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=cea6214f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2907428436159895</a><br />\n<br />\n愛沙尼亞最高蘇維埃唔同意蘇聯最高蘇維埃主席團（*** 三年前）排除愛沙尼亞蘇維埃社會主義共和國民族自決嘅憲法權利，提出蘇聯憲法修正案。依據1966年9月16號關於經濟、社會、文化、公民及政治權利的國際公約（呢份條約亦已獲蘇聯通過認可）及其他國際權利之規範，愛沙尼亞蘇維埃社會主義共和國人民權力嘅最高機構 &mdash; 愛沙尼亞蘇維埃社會主義共和國最高蘇維埃宣布愛沙尼亞蘇維埃社會主義共和國嘅法律比蘇聯法律優先，直至同蘇聯另立條約為止。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯憲法嘅修正案要經愛沙尼亞最高蘇維埃同意，加上愛沙尼亞共和國憲法經相應修訂之後，先會喺愛沙尼亞境內生效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2907312939504778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2907312939504778&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wyTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=3b5678ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2907312939504778</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abF6qTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabF6qTg.jpg&h=d95971a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pp4OEdj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPp4OEdj.jpg&h=a2e943ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8G56qTn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8G56qTn.jpg&h=b2cef5b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8177573fa9528a0941b714440295eda6f21105a2","tid":2312287,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T18:57:51.000Z","msg":"點知佢會同我哋講香港人只係中華民族嘅一部份，到最後愛沙尼亞嗰套民族自決放唔到落嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14435375d46765a6cc0c9a6d17bf776804d2fdcf","tid":2312287,"uid":264158,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T19:48:22.000Z","msg":"一開始個憲法都冇香港人同意"},{"pid":"cee0c436c61bbd0b8ae479b5e53852841eb8bd3c","tid":2312287,"uid":88134,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14435375d46765a6cc0c9a6d17bf776804d2fdcf","tid":2312287,"uid":264158,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T19:48:22.000Z","msg":"一開始個憲法都冇香港人同意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T19:51:27.000Z","msg":"無錯，係夾硬強姦香港人既<br />\n由一開始將香港交俾支那就係錯"},{"pid":"1ccd1f1fc54e52da867b2dc12d78af61d6c04294","tid":2312287,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T20:12:27.000Z","msg":"香港人冇同意過呢個所謂「憲法」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}